/>\n<br />\n但，肯定唔係耶和華條狗屎垃圾蛋散"},{"pid":"3ee25b17ce5644343bda3060f78dbcdc2c04f97d","tid":626071,"uid":144413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"60cabc30857cae70da853d63b50f8d9c0e918ff1","tid":626071,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"847697e1cf19043a087eda42a518932d80267487","tid":626071,"uid":102179,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"3073a1134f3e8bb6c0da273b1b2bb61c8aec3b52","tid":626071,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T03:22:51.000Z","msg":"係一個象徵。<br />\n<br />\n不是夏娃食果之前，人的行為無罪，<br />\n<br />\n而是食果之後，我們知道了甚麼是有罪，而明知故犯，就要贖罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T04:41:03.000Z","msg":"即係未食果之前人類已經有犯緊罪 不過因為唔知所以上帝就唔罰人類 上帝本意創造人類又由佢地犯罪 即係行惡啦"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T04:57:28.000Z","msg":"係自由"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T07:56:35.000Z","msg":"有自由但唔可以犯罪係咩玩法？<br />\n你連善惡嘅界線都分唔清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁樣上帝賦予我哋嘅自由仲係咪真嘅自由？"},{"pid":"e3c92ddc8682133742f29356634153a645b4dcd4","tid":626071,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3ee25b17ce5644343bda3060f78dbcdc2c04f97d","tid":626071,"uid":144413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"60cabc30857cae70da853d63b50f8d9c0e918ff1","tid":626071,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"847697e1cf19043a087eda42a518932d80267487","tid":626071,"uid":102179,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T04:41:03.000Z","msg":"即係未食果之前人類已經有犯緊罪 不過因為唔知所以上帝就唔罰人類 上帝本意創造人類又由佢地犯罪 即係行惡啦"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T04:57:28.000Z","msg":"係自由"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T07:56:35.000Z","msg":"有自由但唔可以犯罪係咩玩法？<br />\n你連善惡嘅界線都分唔清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁樣上帝賦予我哋嘅自由仲係咪真嘅自由？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T08:13:31.000Z","msg":"我地有辨別罪惡既能力，同時有自由去犯罪<br />\n<br />\n耶穌就係為自由而犯了罪既人贖罪"},{"pid":"09d2888d7f7fed1e80d73830b3d856c8f8325403","tid":626071,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"b00dbf29a9bcb8cca2077f264bf0a14339577146","tid":626071,"uid":114275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T07:21:48.000Z","msg":"如果上帝係全能嘅話<br />\n個世界有罪惡就係佢做得唔完美"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T08:45:08.000Z","msg":"完美只係形以上既概念<br />\n<br />\n人對一切事物既定義都係完美，而現實係無<br />\n<br />\n例如無長度無闊度無高度既點、無闊度無高度既線、無高度既面，現實都係唔存在，不過呢個就係歐氏幾何對點線面既定義，咁先係完美既點線面<br />\n<br />\n上帝係咪完美？定義上係，不過現實既上帝一定係比人類更有人性，否則佢唔會賦予到人智慧同人性，所以衪都唔係完美，衪只係比人更有人性，更有智慧"},{"pid":"ca109e341c07321679544956d2486b78506f62b2","tid":626071,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T09:44:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99b08cc6c178b1ba421516df98bb803b260ea50f","tid":626071,"uid":59465,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T09:46:19.000Z","msg":"多謝樓主曲線反耶<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"293829ea3beb67d739c1e9f08b865f8ace927f56","tid":626071,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"99b08cc6c178b1ba421516df98bb803b260ea50f","tid":626071,"uid":59465,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T09:46:19.000Z","msg":"多謝樓主曲線反耶<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T10:43:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1826d1ff3f9a783030a7a724c5d92555b0b1d8a0","tid":626071,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T11:48:57.000Z","msg":"其實解通了所有問題"},{"pid":"a2ab2c995d5526ca9c6889eb091760c327ba9f76","tid":626071,"uid":47392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T13:00:10.000Z","msg":"原罪問題<br />\n人